":2210984,"uid":34990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T17:44:23.000Z","msg":"個位真係住個頭先會行去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係要搞好外賣"},{"pid":"60bc4d0fef145872b3f9b4b6eb095450eec4fce4","tid":2210984,"uid":368777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a91263a5f89b1cebd55bd17267d3a550d9705a1a","tid":2210984,"uid":34990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T17:44:23.000Z","msg":"個位真係住個頭先會行去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係要搞好外賣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T18:06:57.000Z","msg":"唔係路德圍真係有d唔就腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aa3b7c628f0fff385327b0791a26f95ab417b8e","tid":2210984,"uid":201400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T20:55:20.000Z","msg":"之前食過 唔知係太忙定因為趕收工<br />\n叫咗幾款點心 全部都未熟...<br />\n食粒燒賣 一咬落去<br />\n個口感勁粉 即刻吐返出黎<br />\n之後唔敢再食呢間野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日比個機會試多次啦<br />\n<br />\nBtw,呢個鋪位雖然好似睇落幾好<br />\n係正馬路轉角位/係啲商場同住宅附近<br />\n但呢幾年至少執過2-3間鋪..<br />\n我記得嘅就已經有2間小食店/1間日式料理執咗<br />\n唔排除我記性唔好數漏鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9760b9b704924c1651eb709fb14349301cb202ff","tid":2210984,"uid":86643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T20:56:52.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"d6f4f610a35931427e260d33320c0f23865b4b81","tid":2210984,"uid":311328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T21:20:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5748aef127f730079d2dfc1be72b9bcbaf82dd6","tid":2210984,"uid":121145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T18:15:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fd8f71f422da227c85fe9bf182c4fe3adfee59d","tid":2